comments: RAR shows Iguodala (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position and jumps to the side of Paul (HOU) during his jump shot attempt.
LAR and RLS show Harden (HOU) cleanly dislodges the pass from Iguodala (GSW) on the steal attempt.
Green (GSW) engages with Rivers (HOU), but doesn't affect his ability to defend the incoming pass.
Durant (GSW) and Harden (HOU) engage and separate off-ball before Harden's pick.
Rivers (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thompson (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Thompson (GSW) at the end of the drive when he releases from the contact.
Harden (HOU) brings his arm downward and to his left and makes contact to the top of Thompson's (GSW) head/neck area during his follow-through.
Green (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
LAR and RAR show Thompson (GSW) legally contests Harden's (HOU) shot and does not step into his landing area.
LAR and RLS show Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact with Curry (GSW) at the end of the drive, but goes to and not through his body.
Tucker (HOU) makes marginal contact to Green's (GSW) lower body after the release on his driving shot attempt.
Iguodala (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
RLS and RAR show Thompson (GSW) jumps to the side of Harden (HOU) when he contests the jump shot attempt and would have missed him if Harden hadn't extended his legs.
LLS shows Tucker (HOU) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Curry (GSW) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Durant (GSW) makes contact with Gordon (HOU) as he reaches across Gordon's body to get to the ball, affecting his SQBR.
Thompson (GSW) engages and separates with Harden (HOU) and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Iguodala (GSW) and Paul (HOU) engage and separate during the inbound and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Thompson (GSW) moves laterally into Harden's (HOU) path and the contact affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Green (GSW) enters the lane before the release of the free throw.
Paul (HOU) makes incidental contact with Iguodala's (GSW) leg during the rebound following the missed free throw attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Rivers (HOU) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harden (HOU) briefly has an arm around Green (GSW) and a hand to his front, but he releases and does not impede his movement.
Tucker (HOU) briefly engages with Durant (GSW) during the inbound and Durant releases from the contact.
Curry (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Tucker (HOU) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Tucker (HOU) brings his arm across Green's (GSW) body in a continuous motion as Green backpedals towards the perimeter.
Durant (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harden (HOU) during the dribble hand-off and gives Harden room to avoid the contact.
Green (GSW) briefly engages with Tucker (HOU) as the ball is airborne, but disengages as the ball hits the rim and doesn't affect Tucker's ability to rebound.
Durant (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harden (HOU) during the dribble hand-off and gives Harden room to avoid the contact.
Iguodala (GSW) commits a take foul on Paul (HOU).
Tucker (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Durant (GSW).
